videos.headline: Jefferies picks Gabriel in red zone
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel is intercepted by Cam Jefferies who returns it 57 yards to set up Cincinnati in UCF territory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jefferies picks Gabriel in red zone) 2019/10/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder connects with Cloud for Cincy TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder rolls right and finds Trent Cloud in the end zone for a five-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Ridder connects with Cloud for Cincy TD) 2019/10/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCF pass rush forces Ridder into INT
videos.description: Desmond Ridder is hit as he throws and Tay Gowan is there to make the interception for the Knights.

videos.headline: McCrae goes untouched for UCF TD
videos.description: Greg McCrae bounces to the outside and cashes in for a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (McCrae goes untouched for UCF TD) 2019/10/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gardner picks Gabriel for Cincy TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel is intercepted by Ahmad Gardner who returns it 16 yards for a Cincinnati touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Gardner picks Gabriel for Cincy TD) 2019/10/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bearcats extend lead on 11-yard TD pass
videos.description: Desmond Ridder floats one to Alec Pierce for an 11-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Bearcats extend lead on 11-yard TD pass) 2019/10/04 ESHEET
